Class MeaningProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.stewardshipaction.properties.ReferenceableProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.stewardshipaction.properties.MeaningProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MeaningProperties extends ReferenceableProperties
MeaningProperties is a cut-down summary of a glossary term to aid the stewardship action in understanding the content of an asset.
